    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-08-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-08-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="234"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d234">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Herbert</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Private.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">British Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Newport</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-08-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 16, 1892</hi>
                        </date>. (Received August 16.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am privately informed that order in council was passed Saturday abolishing
                    rebate at end of this season. Immediate change impossible, owing to contracts.
                    Hope to make official communication in a day or two.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herbert.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
